---
title: Bang Bang Double Tofu Bowl with Edamame Rice and Avocado Salad
description: This tofu bowl is a festival of flavours! We've stepped up every element of this lively dish. From avocado salad to spicy mayo, each colourful bite is a delight.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-de-tofu-double-bang-bang-80737802.jpg
